    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const item = $json;\nconst systemPrompt = `You are an AI triage assistant for a veterinary clinic called PetCare Medellin.\\n\\nYour task is to classify each incoming message into exactly one of these categories:\\n- URGENCIA\\n- AGENDAMIENTO\\n- CONSULTA\\n- SEGUIMIENTO\\n- ADMINISTRATIVA\\n\\nRules:\\n- Return only valid JSON.\\n- Do not include markdown.\\n- Do not include extra text.\\n- Use exactly these keys: categoria, prioridad, justificacion.\\n- categoria must be one of: URGENCIA, AGENDAMIENTO, CONSULTA, SEGUIMIENTO, ADMINISTRATIVA\\n- prioridad must be one of: ALTA, MEDIA, BAJA\\n- justificacion must be a short sentence in Spanish.\\n- If the message suggests breathing problems, bleeding, seizures, poisoning, severe pain, trauma, collapse, or immediate danger, classify it as URGENCIA with prioridad ALTA.\\n- If the user wants to book, reschedule, or cancel an appointment, classify it as AGENDAMIENTO.\\n- If the user asks for business information or clinical information answerable from knowledge base, classify it as CONSULTA unless it is clearly administrative.\\n- If the user asks about the status of a previous case, request, treatment, or ongoing process, classify it as SEGUIMIENTO.\\n- If the user asks about schedules, billing, payments, location, certificates, or policies, classify it as ADMINISTRATIVA.\\n- If more than one category fits, choose the most operationally urgent one.\\n\\nReturn this exact JSON structure:\\n{\\n  \\\"categoria\\\": \\\"URGENCIA|AGENDAMIENTO|CONSULTA|SEGUIMIENTO|ADMINISTRATIVA\\\",\\n  \\\"prioridad\\\": \\\"ALTA|MEDIA|BAJA\\\",\\n  \\\"justificacion\\\": \\\"motivo breve\\\"\\n}`;\nconst userPrompt = `Clasifica el siguiente mensaje de un usuario de la clinica veterinaria.\\n\\nCanal: ${item.channel}\\nUsuario: ${item.user_name}\\nContacto: ${item.contact}\\nMensaje: ${item.message_text}\\nFecha: ${item.timestamp}\\n\\nDevuelve unicamente JSON valido.`;\nreturn [{ json: { ...item, system_prompt: systemPrompt, user_prompt: userPrompt } }];"
      },
      "id": "build-prompts",
      "name": "Build Triage Prompts",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        940,
